question: who bought IFONE in BESTBYU
query: SELECT distinct T1.name FROM customers AS T1 JOIN sales AS T2 ON T1.customer_id  =  T2.customer_id JOIN sales_details AS T3 ON T2.sales_id  =  T3.sales_id JOIN shops AS T4 ON T2.shop_id  =  T4.shop_id JOIN products AS T5 ON T3.product_id  =  T5.product_id WHERE T4.name  =  'BESTBYU' AND T5.type  =  'IFONE'

question: Who bought WINDOOWS in BESTBYU
query: SELECT T1.name FROM customers AS T1 JOIN sales AS T2 ON T1.customer_id  =  T2.customer_id JOIN sales_details AS T3 ON T2.sales_id  =  T3.sales_id JOIN products AS T4 on T4.product_id  =  T3.product_id JOIN shops as T5 ON T2.shop_id  =  T5.shop_id WHERE T4.type  =  'WINDOOWS' AND T5.name  =  'BESTBYU'

question: What phone number does Mary has?
query: SELECT T1.phone_nr FROM customers AS T1 WHERE T1.name  =  'Mary'

question: show price, type, address of the shop of the products that are in stock with a price higher than 300 in BESTBYU
query: SELECT T1.type , T1.price, T3.address FROM products AS T1 JOIN stock AS T2 ON T1.product_id  =  T2.product_id JOIN shops AS T3 ON T2.shop_id  =  T3.shop_id WHERE T1.price  >=  300 AND T3.name  =  'BESTBYU'

question: how many SANSUMG products are on stock
query: SELECT SUM ( T1.quantity )  from stock AS T1 JOIN products AS T2 ON T1.product_id  =  T2.product_id JOIN manufacturers AS T3 ON T2.manufacturer_id  =  T3.manufacturer_id where T3.name  =  'SANSUMG'

question: which ANAPPLE product has price higher than GALAZYTAB?
query: SELECT T1.type FROM products AS T1 JOIN manufacturers AS T2 ON T1.manufacturer_id  =  T2.manufacturer_id WHERE T1.price  >   ( SELECT T3.price from products AS T3 where T3.type  =  'GALAZYTAB' )  and T2.name  =  'ANAPPLE'

question: what is total amount of sales for Richard
query: SELECT SUM ( T1.sum_total )  FROM sales AS T1 join customers AS T2 ON T1.customer_id  =  T2.customer_id where T2.name  =  'Richard'

question: show me customer names
query: SELECT T1.name FROM customers AS T1

question: What are the phone numbers of the customers?
query: SELECT T1.phone_nr FROM customers AS T1

question: show customer names and shop names where customer bought products and dates of purchase
query: SELECT T1.name, T3.name, T2.date FROM customers AS T1 JOIN sales AS T2 ON T1.customer_id  =  T2.customer_id JOIN shops AS T3 ON T2.shop_id  =  T3.shop_id

question: How many IFONE are sold in a shop in New York?
query: SELECT SUM ( T2.quantity )  FROM products AS T1 join sales_details AS T2 ON T1.product_id  =  T2.product_id JOIN sales AS T3 ON T2.sales_id  =  T3.sales_id JOIN shops AS T4 ON T3.shop_id  =  T4.shop_id where T4.address  =  'New York' and T1.type  =  'IFONE'

question: show me customer name, phone number and address
query: SELECT T1.name, T1.phone_nr, T1.address FROM customers AS T1

question: how many products have price higher than 500
query: SELECT COUNT ( T1.type )  FROM products AS T1 where T1.price  >  500

question: show me total amound of sales for each shop id
query: SELECT SUM ( T1.SUM_TOTAL ) ,T1.shop_id FROM sales AS T1 group by T1.shop_id

question: what manufacturer manufactures IFONE
query: SELECT T1.name FROM manufacturers AS T1 JOIN products as T2 ON T1.manufacturer_id  =  T2.manufacturer_id WHERE T2.type  =  'IFONE'

question: what shop does stock SURFAS?
query: SELECT T1.name FROM shops AS T1 JOIN stock AS T2 ON T1.shop_id  =  T2.shop_id JOIN products AS T3 ON T2.product_id  =  T3.product_id WHERE T3.type  =  'SURFAS'

question: what products were sold between 2016-01-01 and 2016-12-31; 2016-01-01#date#date; 2016-12-31#date#date
query: select distinct T2.PRODUCT_ID from SALES AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID where T1.DATE  >=  '2016-01-01' and T1.DATE  <=  '2016-12-31'

question: how many products are sold that have prices greater than 200 dollars between 2017-12-01 and 2017-12-31; 200#number#number; 2017-12-01#date#date; 2017-12-31#date#date
query: select distinct sum ( T2.QUANTITY )  from PRODUCTS AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.PRODUCT_ID  =  T2.PRODUCT_ID JOIN SALES AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID where T3.DATE  >=  '2017-12-01' and T3.DATE  <=  '2017-12-31' and T1.PRICE  >  200

question: what is quantity of sales from 2011-01-01 to 2012-12-31; 2011-01-01#date#date; 2012-12-31#date#date
query: select distinct sum ( T2.QUANTITY )  from SALES AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID where T1.DATE  >=  '2011-01-01' and T1.DATE  <=  '2012-12-31'

question: how many customers bought MACBUK before 2017-07-04; 2017-07-04#date#date
query: select count ( distinct T3.CUSTOMER_ID )  from PRODUCTS AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.PRODUCT_ID  =  T2.PRODUCT_ID JOIN SALES AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID where T3.DATE  <  '2017-07-04' and T1.TYPE  =  'MACBUK'

question: How many customers bought IFONE at BESTBYU between 2017-12-25 and 2017-12-25; 2017-12-25#date#date
query: select count ( distinct T2.CUSTOMER_ID )  from SHOPS AS T1 JOIN SALES AS T2 on T1.SHOP_ID  =  T2.SHOP_ID JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID JOIN PRODUCTS AS T4 on T3.PRODUCT_ID  =  T4.PRODUCT_ID where T4.TYPE  =  'IFONE' and T1.NAME  =  'BESTBYU' and T2.DATE  >=  '2017-12-25' and T2.DATE  <=  '2017-12-25'

question: how many products were bought by each customer between 2015-01-01 and 2015-12-31 in shops located in New York; 2015-01-01#date#date; 2015-12-31#date#date
query: select distinct sum ( T3.QUANTITY ) , T2.CUSTOMER_ID from SHOPS AS T1 JOIN SALES AS T2 on T1.SHOP_ID  =  T2.SHOP_ID JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID where T2.DATE  >=  '2015-01-01' and T2.DATE  <=  '2015-12-31' and T1.ADDRESS  =  'New York' group by T2.CUSTOMER_ID

question: what is GALAZY sales between 2014-01-01 and 2014-12-31; 2014-01-01#date#date; 2014-12-31#date#date
query: select distinct sum ( T3.SUM_TOTAL )  from PRODUCTS AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.PRODUCT_ID  =  T2.PRODUCT_ID JOIN SALES AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID where T1.TYPE  =  'GALAZY' and T3.DATE  >=  '2014-01-01' and T3.DATE  <=  '2014-12-31'
